{"id": "sgo1665703135121", "title": "ulistdel", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "API Reference", "APIs: 3GL Functions", "ulistdel"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgo1665703135121.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">ulistdel</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: ulist2uf \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: ulist2uf \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/voy1665703134785.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: ulistget \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: ulistget \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvk1665703134983.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgo1665703135121.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgo1665703135121.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgo1665703135121.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531961\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531961\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sgo1665703135121.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sgo1665703135121.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sgo1665703135121.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sgo1665703135121\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__ulistdel_405366\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Delete an item from an item list.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__topic_d121808e1_d121809e1_d121810e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sgo1665703135121_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__codeblock_ez1_vxc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long ulistdel (UHACThList, intoption, intindex, UCHAR*Id);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__topic_d86362e1_d86363e1_d86364e1_d86365e1_d86366e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212765e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__parml_sjk_wxc_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hList</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Handle to the list, as returned by <code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistnew</code>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">option</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Yype of item to be deleted. Possible values are:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__ul_ewt_yxc_bwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__li_d45332e1_d45333e1_d45334e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121823e1_d121824e1_d121825e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UITEM_OPTION_NONE</code>—deletes an indexed item. You must\n                           supply a value for <var class=\"keyword varname\">index</var>; the value for\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var> is ignored.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__li_d45335e1_d45336e1_d45337e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121826e1_d121827e1_d121828e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UITEM_OPTION_ID</code>—deletes an associative item. You must\n                           supply a value for <var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var>; the value for\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">index</var> is ignored.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__li_d45338e1_d45339e1_d45340e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121829e1_d121830e1_d121831e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UITEM_OPTION_ID_CASE</code>—as\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">UITEM_OPTION_ID</code>, except that the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var>\n                           is handled in a case-sensitive manner (for example, deleting an item with\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var> \"<code class=\"ph codeph\">a</code>\" does not delete an item\n                           with <var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var> \"<code class=\"ph codeph\">A</code>\").</p>\n</li>\n</ul></dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">index</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Index of the item, if the item is indexed</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">ID of the item, if the item is associative</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__topic_d86367e1_d86368e1_d86369e1_d86370e1_d86371e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212765e173\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by ulistdel</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__2\">Success.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__1\">-165</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__2\">The supplied handle <var class=\"keyword varname\">hList</var> is\n                        not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__1\">-1112</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__2\">The value of <var class=\"keyword varname\">option</var> is not\n                        valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__1\">-1203</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__2\">The value of <var class=\"keyword varname\">id</var> is out of\n                        range.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__1\">-1406</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgo1665703135121__table_d14903e1_d14904e1_d14905e1__entry__2\">Memory could not be allocated or freed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__topic_d86372e1_d86373e1_d86374e1_d86375e1_d86376e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212765e261\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__topic_d86377e1_d86378e1_d86379e1_d86380e1_d86381e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212765e273\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121850e1_d121851e1_d121852e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistdel</code> deletes an item from the\n            specified list. This function is very similar to the ProcScript command\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">delitem</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121853e1_d121854e1_d121855e1\">The variable <var class=\"keyword varname\">option</var> determines\n            if the item is indexed or associative.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121856e1_d121857e1_d121858e1\">Note that there is no safeguard if you do not\n            provide the expected parameters. For example, if you use\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">UITEM_OPTION_NONE</code> but fail to supply a value for\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var>, your program is likely to crash.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__p_d121859e1_d121860e1_d121861e1\">It is allowed, although not recommended, to mix\n            indexed and associative items in one list. For example, you can remove an item by its\n            index from a list that contains only associative items (but not the other way\n            around).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__section_e3v_hyc_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212765e305\">Example:  ulistnew, ulist2uf, ulistdel, and ulistput</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example creates an associative list, consisting of country\n            codes and names, and passes it to a service, which prints it to the message frame. The\n            operation DOLIST in service TESTSVC is defined as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sgo1665703135121_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__codeblock_nnl_jyc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation dolist\nparams\nstring thelist : in;\nendparams\nputmess \"%%thelist\"\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The 3GL code that creates the list and passes it to service DOLIST is as\n            follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sgo1665703135121_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__codeblock_i4s_kyc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">char *countries[] = {\n\n\"NL\", \"Netherlands\",\n\"GB\", \"Great Britain\",\n\"D\", \"Germany\",\n\"F\", \"France\",\n\"?\", \"huh?\",\n\"I\", \"Italy\",\n\"E\", \"Spain\",\n0 };\n\n#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nvoid pass_itemlist ()\n{\nUHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */\nUHACT hOp; /* Operation handles for OP1 amd OP2 */\nlong actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */\nUHACT hList; /* Item list handle */\nint i; /* Loop variable */\n\nueopen(&amp;hEnv); /* Get environment handle */\nuinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0,\nUDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn, &amp;procErr);/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */\n\nuinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"DOLIST\", 0, &amp;hOp);/* Instantiate operation DOLIST*/\nulistnew(hEnv, &amp;hList); /* Create an item list */\n\nfor ( i=0; countries[i]; i+= 2 ) /* Loop through the data */\n{\nulistput(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0,\ncountries[i], countries[i+1] ); /* Add the list item */\n}\n\nulistdel(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, \"?\");/* Delete the item with id \"?\" */\nulist2uf(hOp, 1, hList); /* Copy item list to operation param*/\nuopract(hOp, &amp;actStatus, &amp;procErr); /* Activate the operation */\n\nuinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Destroy instance */\nufreeh (&amp;hList); /* Free list handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hOp); /* Free operation handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hIn); /* Free instance handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hEnv); /* Free environment handle */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation DOLIST prints this line to the message frame:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sgo1665703135121_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sgo1665703135121__codeblock_pd5_myc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">NL=Netherlands;GB=Great Britain;D=Germany;F=France;I=Italy;E=Spain\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nci1665702692918.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ulistput</a><p>Insert an item into an item list.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lqw1719402294611.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>delitem</a><p>Deletes an item from a list.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531961\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531961\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ulistdel Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete an item from an item list. Explain this code long ulistdel (UHACThList, intoption, intindex, UCHAR*Id); Copy Parameters hList Handle to the list, as returned by ulistnew option Yype of item to be deleted. Possible values are: UITEM_OPTION_NONE —deletes an indexed item. You must supply a value for index ; the value for Id is ignored. UITEM_OPTION_ID —deletes an associative item. You must supply a value for Id ; the value for index is ignored. UITEM_OPTION_ID_CASE —as UITEM_OPTION_ID , except that the Id is handled in a case-sensitive manner (for example, deleting an item with Id \" a \" does not delete an item with Id \" A \"). index Index of the item, if the item is indexed Id ID of the item, if the item is associative Return Values Table 1. Values returned by ulistdel Value Meaning 0 Success. -165 The supplied handle hList is not valid. -1112 The value of option is not valid. -1203 The value of id is out of range. -1406 Memory could not be allocated or freed. Use Library: ucall Description ulistdel deletes an item from the specified list. This function is very similar to the ProcScript command delitem . The variable option determines if the item is indexed or associative. Note that there is no safeguard if you do not provide the expected parameters. For example, if you use UITEM_OPTION_NONE but fail to supply a value for Id , your program is likely to crash. It is allowed, although not recommended, to mix indexed and associative items in one list. For example, you can remove an item by its index from a list that contains only associative items (but not the other way around). Example: ulistnew, ulist2uf, ulistdel, and ulistput The following example creates an associative list, consisting of country codes and names, and passes it to a service, which prints it to the message frame. The operation DOLIST in service TESTSVC is defined as follows: Explain this code operation dolist params string thelist : in; endparams putmess \"%%thelist\" end Copy The 3GL code that creates the list and passes it to service DOLIST is as follows: Explain this code char *countries[] = { \"NL\", \"Netherlands\", \"GB\", \"Great Britain\", \"D\", \"Germany\", \"F\", \"France\", \"?\", \"huh?\", \"I\", \"Italy\", \"E\", \"Spain\", 0 }; #include <h3gl.h> void pass_itemlist () { UHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */ UHACT hOp; /* Operation handles for OP1 amd OP2 */ long actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */ UHACT hList; /* Item list handle */ int i; /* Loop variable */ ueopen(&hEnv); /* Get environment handle */ uinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn, &procErr);/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */ uinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"DOLIST\", 0, &hOp);/* Instantiate operation DOLIST*/ ulistnew(hEnv, &hList); /* Create an item list */ for ( i=0; countries[i]; i+= 2 ) /* Loop through the data */ { ulistput(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, countries[i], countries[i+1] ); /* Add the list item */ } ulistdel(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, \"?\");/* Delete the item with id \"?\" */ ulist2uf(hOp, 1, hList); /* Copy item list to operation param*/ uopract(hOp, &actStatus, &procErr); /* Activate the operation */ uinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Destroy instance */ ufreeh (&hList); /* Free list handle */ ufreeh (&hOp); /* Free operation handle */ ufreeh (&hIn); /* Free instance handle */ ufreeh (&hEnv); /* Free environment handle */ } Copy The operation DOLIST prints this line to the message frame: Explain this code NL=Netherlands;GB=Great Britain;D=Germany;F=France;I=Italy;E=Spain Copy Related Links ulistput Insert an item into an item list. delitem Deletes an item from a list. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}